song_name: Perempuan Paling Cantik Di Negeriku Indonesia

version_description: 1st version have comment to improve, so I give some improve, and Chord more complete.
This song brings some beautiful memory to me and I'm sure to a lot of people.
If you're using an electric guitar (with distortion), try out to play in powerchords [F to F5, C to C5, ...] Please give me feedback and a rating. Have Fun :).
This is the chord version from the original, so there is not so much variety in it cause it's all in Cm. If you're on an electric guitar then try to use powerchords, if you want.
